info:
The APCO internship is designed to give interns a valuable educational experience, with exposure to a wide range of client work. While APCO interns are encouraged to develop their interest in either public relations or government relations, they will gain exposure in both practice areas. Outstanding interns may be given the opportunity to transition to permanent, full-time employment. 

The following are specific duties assigned to interns and are performed on a daily basis:
-News monitoring and analysis ;
-Conducting research for existing projects and new business opportunities ;
-Providing support in content drafting, media relations, online community engagement and event management ;
-Assisting with business proposal development ;
-Active participation in brainstorming and strategy planning sessions;
-Performing similar duties as assigned

Requirements & qualifications:
-Education: Bachelor or master's degree in progress, preferably in communications, journalism, advertising, marketing, political science or related fields
-Experience: Relevant internship experience preferred

Core Skills:
-Strong interest in pursuing a career in corporate communications and/or government relations;
-Reliable, detail-oriented, and with analytical thinking;
-Able to balance multiple tasks and work in a fast-paced environment
-Able to work as in a team and independently;
-Extensive knowledge of Microsoft Office Suite;
-Proficiency with design and video editing tools (e.g. Photoshop, InDesign, Illustrator and Premiere) preferred;
-Languages: Excellent written and oral communication skills in Mandarin and English required
-The Intern should be able to make a commitment to an internship for 3-6 months and spend at least 3 full working days per week in the office.

岗位职责：
1、直播前调试设备、与主播确认直播流程，参与话术输出;
2、直播中进行话术配合，促单和辅助讲解，避免冷场;
3、及时与主播沟通，监管弹幕内容，保证直播间弹幕秩序；
3、根据直播实时效果反馈，配合主播进行现场直播节奏调整;
4、直播后记录整理直播数据，复盘整理；
5、配合其他临时需求;样品道具管理、短视频拍摄;
6、及时掌握市场信息，了解平台新规则、新活动、新玩法；
7、密切关注店铺评分，有任何异常及时反馈;

任职要求：
1、具备强烈的自我驱动力，良好的沟通能力，应变能力，团队协作精神。
2、电商直播中控/场控经验，有拆解对标账号的能力;
3、熟悉视频号最新运营玩法及直播规则及优化技巧;
4、可以接受灵活排班制，跟着直播时间调整;
5、有责任心，具备良好的分析判断和独立思考能力，严谨细致;

Overview


	TrailRunner International, a top global full-service
communications firm, is seeking to hire a PR Analyst Intern to support the
growth of TRI’s business in greater China. This position has a chance to be our
full-time employee after your graduation. This intern role will offer exciting
growth potential and valuable opportunities to learn and execute important
work. 

 This position will: 
 1. Collaborate closely with team members on proposals and client work
2. Deliver valuable market intelligence through research and analysis

 Job Responsibilities:




			Assist in daily media monitoring of news stories and industry trends; 




			Doing research and present it in concise and executive format; 




			Help to create market briefs on various industries and companies ; 




			Translate, localize and write content for press releases, market briefs, social media articles and posts, media monitoring reports; 




			Support team members on proposals and client work as needed. 








	Requirements: 




			Bachelor’s degree or above, Major in communications, public relations, media, business, digital; 




			Can take internship at least 3 months, work at least 3 days per week, start in Feb; 




			Interest in global affairs, corporate affairs, financial, tech and business news media across China and Asia; 




			You are focused, results-oriented, driven to succeed; 




			You are proactive, energetic, diligent and curious; 




			You have a positive attitude and enjoy teamwork; 




			Business level proficiency in English and native Chinese language skills required.
